text: KICK may refer to: * KICK (AM), a radio station (1340 AM) licensed to serve Springfield, Missouri, United States * KICK-FM, a radio station (97.9 FM) licensed to Palmyra, Missouri * CKIC-FM, a radio station (92.9 FM) licensed to Winnipeg, Manitoba, Canada, branded as KICK-FM * Karate International Council of Kickboxing * KICK (Detroit), a Michigan non-profit business ==See also== * Kick (disambiguation)
title: KICK
